    If you feel you can book your own appointment, but don't know where to start, check out the Self-Booking Resources located in the navigation menu, or click <%= link_to "here", resources_path, class: 'font-bold' %>.
    </h3>
    <h3 class="sm:text-xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-tight mt-2">
    We’re happy you found your way to us! 
    </h3>

    <div class="text-gray-900 mt-4">
